---
// Process component showing our methodology
---

<section id="process" class="process section-animate">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="process-layout">
      <div class="process-text">
        <h2>From bottleneck to business win in 4–8 weeks.</h2>
        <p class="section-description">We've productized our approach so you always know where you stand.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="step card-animate step-1">
          <div class="icon-placeholder">1</div>
          <h3>Discovery Sprint (1–2 Weeks)</h3>
          <p>We map your workflows and pinpoint the 3–5 highest-ROI fixes. If we don't find opportunities worth pursuing, you pay nothing.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step card-animate step-2">
          <div class="icon-placeholder">2</div>
          <h3>Pilot Build (2–4 Weeks)</h3>
          <p>We design and deploy your first automation — tackling the most painful bottleneck head-on. From day one, it delivers measurable savings.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step card-animate step-3">
          <div class="icon-placeholder">3</div>
          <h3>Implementation & Enablement</h3>
          <p>We roll out additional solutions, provide your team with simple guides, and stay on hand for refinement — ensuring long-term ROI.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process {
    background-color: #F8F9FA;
  }

  .process-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4.2rem; /* 5% larger: 4rem to 4.2rem */
    align-items: start;
  }

  .process-text {
    grid-column: 1;
    grid-row: 1;
  }

  .process-text h2 {
    font-size: 2.625rem; /* 5% larger: 2.5rem to 2.625rem */
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.575rem; /* 5% larger: 1.5rem to 1.575rem */
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.575rem; /* 5% larger: 1.5rem to 1.575rem */
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 500px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .process-grid {
    grid-column: 2;
    grid-row: 1;
    position: relative;
    height: 600px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .step {
    position: absolute;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 2.625rem; /* 5% larger: 2.5rem to 2.625rem */
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 12.6px; /* 5% larger: 12px to 12.6px */
    box-shadow: 0 6.3px 31.5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* 5% larger shadows */
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    width: 320px;
    max-width: 320px;
  }

  .step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8.4px); /* 5% larger: -8px to -8.4px */
    box-shadow: 0 12.6px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); /* 5% larger shadows */
  }

  .step-1 {
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
  }

  .step-2 {
    top: 200px;
    left: 100px;
  }

  .step-3 {
    top: 400px;
    left: 200px;
  }

  .icon-placeholder {
    width: 84px; /* 5% larger: 80px to 84px */
    height: 84px; /* 5% larger: 80px to 84px */
    background: var(--accent-blue);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2.1rem; /* 5% larger: 2rem to 2.1rem */
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2.1rem; /* 5% larger: 2rem to 2.1rem */
  }

  .step h3 {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 1.575rem; /* 5% larger: 1.5rem to 1.575rem */
  }

  .step p {
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.155rem; /* 5% larger: 1.1rem to 1.155rem */
  }

  @media (min-width: 1920px) {
    .step {
      padding: 3.675rem; /* 5% larger: 3.5rem to 3.675rem */
      width: 360px;
      max-width: 360px;
    }

    .icon-placeholder {
      width: 105px; /* 5% larger: 100px to 105px */
      height: 105px; /* 5% larger: 100px to 105px */
      font-size: 2.625rem; /* 5% larger: 2.5rem to 2.625rem */
    }

    .section-description {
      font-size: 1.8375rem; /* 5% larger: 1.75rem to 1.8375rem */
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.1rem; /* 5% larger: 2rem to 2.1rem */
    }

    .process-text {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: 1;
    }

    .process-grid {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: 2;
      height: auto;
      position: relative;
    }

    .section-description {
      font-size: 1.155rem; /* 5% larger: 1.1rem to 1.155rem */
      margin-bottom: 3.15rem; /* 5% larger: 3rem to 3.15rem */
    }

    .step {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: none;
      margin-bottom: 2.1rem; /* 5% larger: 2rem to 2.1rem */
      padding: 1.575rem; /* 5% larger: 1.5rem to 1.575rem */
    }

    .step-1,
    .step-2,
    .step-3 {
      top: auto;
      left: auto;
    }

    .icon-placeholder {
      width: 47.25px; /* 5% larger: 45px to 47.25px */
      height: 47.25px; /* 5% larger: 45px to 47.25px */
      font-size: 1.155rem; /* 5% larger: 1.1rem to 1.155rem */
      margin-bottom: 1.05rem; /* 5% larger: 1rem to 1.05rem */
    }
  }
</style>
